{"metadata":{"name":"Sunan Abu Dawud","section":{"35":"Combing the Hair (Kitab Al-Tarajjul)"}},"hadiths":[{"hadithnumber":4187,"arabicnumber":4187,"text":"حدثنا ابن نفيل، حدثنا عبد الرحمن بن أبي الزناد، عن هشام بن عروة، عن أبيه، عن عائشة، قالت كان شعر رسول الله صلى الله عليه وسلم فوق الوفرة ودون الجمة ‏.‏","grades":[{"name":"Al-Albani","grade":"Hasan Sahih"},{"name":"Muhammad Muhyi Al-Din Abdul Hamid","grade":"Hasan Sahih"},{"name":"Shuaib Al Arnaut","grade":"Sahih Lighairihi"},{"name":"Zubair Ali Zai","grade":"Isnaad Hasan"}],"reference":{"book":35,"hadith":29}}]}